FBIS3-18306 "drweu040_l_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 SPAIN Algerian Aircraft Hijacked to Alicante LD2802132194 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1300 GMT 28 Feb 94 LD2802132194 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] An Algerian aircraft is being held at l'Altet airport in Alicante, apparently hijacked by one or several persons. The latest details from Rafael Bermejo. [Bermejo] Good afternoon. Sources at Alicante airport have confirmed to Radio Nacional de Espana the presence of the Algerian airlines -- Air Algerie -- aircraft at this airport. It is now known that it is a Boeing 727, registration 7TVB. The aircraft was reportedly on a domestic flight in Algeria, and according to various sources -- without official confirmation yet -- the hijackers are supposedly three in number, and they are in constant touch with Alicante airport. The number of passengers on the hijkacked aircraft is not known at present.
